Ruby/GIO
========


Ruby/GIO is a Ruby binding of gio-2.0.x.

Requirements
------------

	Ruby:		http://www.ruby-lang.org/
	GIO:	        http://library.gnome.org/devel/gio/stable

Install
-------

	0. install Ruby and GLib.
	1. ruby extconf.rb
	2. make
	3. su
	4. make install

